{"tid":2172305,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：藍絲滋擾之鋒  PoPo背後發功？（李八方）","createTime":"2020-08-24T13:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T13:47:28.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4c4305ced006a5c23391156dd1877dd1e2ada645","tid":2172305,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/PDIIEGABABBV5MWTI3SPWE5FH4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FPDIIEGABABBV5MWTI3SPWE5FH4%2F&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbm1VrQWH3Jev0gRtxLi1IiE%3D&h=7d2fcee0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FPDIIEGABABBV5MWTI3SPWE5FH4%2F&h=e15c5828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/PDIIEGABABBV5MWTI3SPWE5FH4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：藍絲滋擾之鋒 <br />\nPoPo背後發功？（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n前香港眾志秘書長黃之鋒繼日前遭到疑似國安跟蹤後，噚日下午佢趁周日同朋友上山頂放狗期間，點知又遇到冇品藍絲大媽跟蹤兼滋擾。之鋒後來發現，呢個表面上係冇品藍絲大媽，其實可能係同警察有關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/eto_EcAqMDI6JzHepoApW2d4oTs=/1688x1450/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CYLU23AZNZEI7DYMQVG2PPFVHE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Feto_EcAqMDI6JzHepoApW2d4oTs%3D%2F1688x1450%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCYLU23AZNZEI7DYMQVG2PPFVHE.jpg&h=ee0415b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■之鋒（左一）噚日上山頂放狗，遭多名藍絲跟蹤指罵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警長私家車玩跟蹤<br />\n<br />\n話說之鋒，噚日同朋友去到山頂放狗時，突然遭到六名藍絲上前包圍指罵，其中一名藍絲大媽更全程粗口爛舌，一邊舉機、一邊辱罵之鋒同佢朋友，令到之鋒都忍唔住上前理論，力斥對方：「真係好冇品、好低質。」<br />\n<br />\n之鋒喺fb直播片段話，呢班藍絲聲稱自己唔係記者，亦都唔係國安，但就唔知點解喺山頂全程跟蹤滋擾佢。據之鋒嘅片中所見，呢。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n呢班藍絲為乜會咁得閒搞之鋒大半日？之鋒之後查跟蹤佢架車嘅車輛登記地址，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n李八方"},{"pid":"28753fbbca867bd9dab3413136262c523942b2f3","tid":2172305,"uid":165749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T13:47:28.000Z","msg":"政治中立？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}